law.catch_line: Prisoner paroled or under postincarceration supervision subject to orders of board.
law.text: During the period of his or her parole or postincarceration supervision, the prisoner shall be amenable to the orders of the board and the department.
law.history: Amended 2011 Ky. Acts ch.2, sec.89, effective March 3, 2011. -- Amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 211, sec. 108, effective July 14, 1992. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 344, sec. 45, effective July 15, 1982. -- Created 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 82, sec. 3.
